{"id": "1481210093310578870", "channel_id": "1481210093310578870", "type": 0, "author_id": "302718766289256448", "author_name": "zekiei", "author_bot": false, "content": "Brace for some banter, I wanted to talk about the characters the use their realms in a unique way, and the new divine realm mechanic <:Corpo_advance:1459080545882341376> (<= with Corpo appreciation even if she's not in this discussion)\n\n# Characters that use their realms in a unique way\nI **love** when a character uses their relm in a unique way, but it's sadly (besides aequor divine) mostly an old character thing, as per the candidates:\n-# please do tell if I forgor anyone!\n\n### Chaos\n* Change how it plays for everyone\n    * GRamona: Changes the next posse utilisation (*Minor*) \n* Change for themselves\n    * Tawil: The huge keyflare gen is now a ressource to play cards\n    * GRamona: Posse usage now is a damage scaling\n    * 24 (pure Chaos): Posse usage now is a damage scaling\n\n### Aequor\n* Change how it plays for everyone\n    * Gmurphy: Divine Aequor\n    * Vortice: Divine Aequor\n* Change for themselves\n    * Vortice: Can 'devour' tentacles for damage scaling\n\n### Caro\n* Change how it plays for everyone\n     * Thais: Scions double the devour realm mechanic\n* Change for themselves\n    * Salvador: Uses the furnace as a potential damage scaling source\n    * Sorel: devour as many embryos as possible as a damage scaling\n\n### Ultra\n* Change how it plays for everyone\n     * Cassiah: The untra bar is now really a place to store useful skills to get back\n* Change for themselves:\n    * Daffodil: quicker ultra turn access\n    * Liz: Cards upgardes in ultra bar\n    * Erica: I think she does smth with ultra bar and 0cost? but can't remember lmao", "timestamp": "2026-03-11T08:40:05.798000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "ramona_wisdom", "emoji_id": "1468258669341966452", "count": 4}], "attachments": [{"id": "1481210093533138955", "filename": "d80b7c14ff156e65.webp", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 55108}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1481210179080028303", "channel_id": "1481210093310578870", "type": 0, "author_id": "302718766289256448", "author_name": "zekiei", "author_bot": false, "content": "# Divine realms Ideas\nI do like the divine realm mechanic, as it could open new teambuilding possibilites and potential, lets make some funnsies of what it could look like\n\n### Chaos\nAt the begining of the battle, choose 2 uncarried posse. every time you use the posse, you can choose between your original posse and the 2 chosen. the second posse does not offer the possibility to chose any of them, but repeat this effect. there is no limit to posse usage per turn\n\n### Caro\nEmbryo crushing:\nYou can use up your embryo fusion bar to refill furnace (3T cooldown)\n\nEmbryo synthesis:\nYou can use up your furnace to fill the embryo fusion bar (3T cooldown)\n\n### Ultra\nThe ultra bar do not have a max space anymore and can grow infinitely.\n\nMass annihilate:\nThe annihilation button now removes all the cards in ultra bar and give that many insights\n\nBroken turn:\nat any moment, you can go in ultra turn. The damage, healing, shielding, aliemus generation, keyflare generation is equal to (20% x the number of cards in ultra bar) \n-# so 5 cards is your usual pure ultra turn, 1 is weak af but some characters could use it, and its possible to stack 10+ cards to have a crazy ultra turn", "timestamp": "2026-03-11T08:40:26.247000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
{"id": "1481210249707913248", "channel_id": "1481210093310578870", "type": 0, "author_id": "302718766289256448", "author_name": "zekiei", "author_bot": false, "content": "# Character-specific interaction that would be cool\n\n* Caro enabling non caro charcter to have a devour effect\n* Caro using embryo bar for something else than filling it faster\n* Caro able to fuse embryos together in unholy flesh amalgamation that does X time the effect of devour and aliemus\n* Ultra able to \"devour\" either Insights or card in the bar to have some bonus effect\n* Aequor that can make a temp tent into perma tent\n* Aequor that can make perma tent into X temp tents\n* Chaos replacing Posse by a unique effect", "timestamp": "2026-03-11T08:40:43.086000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
